### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:44346
@accessToken = your-access-token-here

### ============================================
### ORGANIZATION APIs
### ============================================

### 1. Check Setup Status (Public)
# @name setupStatus
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Organization/setup-status
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Complete Initial Setup (Public, One-time)
# @name initialSetup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Organization/initial-setup
Content-Type: application/json

