### 3. Get Organization Info (Public)
# @name orgInfo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Organization/info
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get Organization Details (SuperAdmin Only)
# @name getOrganization
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Organization
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5. Update Organization (SuperAdmin Only)
# @name updateOrganization
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/Organization
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

